sources.description:
Jurassic Attack - While returning from a military expedition a helicopter crash lands a   commando unit in a dense, remote tropical jungle - a lost world   populated by dinosaurs. Now they must find a way out of this isolated   valley before becoming prey for prehistoric predators.
2013.  Stars: Gary Stretch, Corin Nemec, Vernon Wells
